{
  "chapter": 91,
  "chapter_summary": "田单亲至寝室探望董匡（项少龙），旁敲侧击试探其来历与能力，招揽他为齐国练兵，董匡以先父遗命为由婉拒，田单临走突抛\"偷袭者与项少龙无关\"之语后离去。晚饭时善柔、赵致等人因即将行动心事重重，善柔率先回房休息养精蓄锐。刘巢带来乐乘行踪情报，揭露乐乘曾与赵穆轮奸舒儿致死的惨事，项少龙悲愤交加。二更时分，精兵团在长街设伏，善柔率先从天而降发动突袭，弩箭齐发射马不取人，飞刀掷击溃敌阵形。乐乘试图退入横巷被荆俊截回，最终善柔抢在项少龙前斩下乐乘首级，乌卓拾起首级下令撤退，整个行动不到半盏茶工夫。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄贵体如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "由于最近生活荒唐，酒色过度，只浸了一会儿河水，便受寒凉所侵。噢！田相请坐！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "很多时我欢喜站着来说话。嘿！看董兄两眼神光照人，怎会是酒色过度的人？只是一时用尽力道，故易受湿寒侵体吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "看来是这样了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄手下的儿郎们，是否由董兄一手训练出来的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "要养马，首先要防范别人来偷马，南方多蛮夷，所以鄙人每天都训练他们，好作防备。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若董兄能把我大齐的兵将，练成像董兄手下儿郎们那样悍不畏死的菁英，虎狼之秦何足惧哉？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "鄙人明白，田相请给董某一点时间。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我明白董兄乃忠于情义的人，否则亦不会舍命救回龙阳君。换了谁在那种情况，都只会自行逃命。",
      "tone": "欣然",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "当时鄙人绝没有想过其他事，只知同舟共济，应付危难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听龙阳君说，董兄当时早有所觉，未知董兄为何能有此先见之明？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "或者是与马儿相处久矣，沾染了点它们敏锐的灵觉，其实每逢有大灾难来临，甚或天气的突然转变，上至飞禽走兽，下至蛇虫蝼蚁，均有异样举动。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄确是非常之人，今天偷袭的主使者不知走了什么倒霉运，竟遇上董兄，致功亏一篑。以董兄如此人才，楚王考烈或者会看走眼，但春申君黄歇怎会把你轻轻放过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "春申君恐怕连我的样子是怎样都记不清楚，有什么放过不放过？董某对楚人早已心淡，再不愿想起他们。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "楚人目光短浅，只求眼前安逸，又屡错不改，确是不值一提。但若楚国落入李园掌握中，董兄认为会出现一番怎样的局面呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "李园此人薄情寡恩，心胸狭窄，纵情酒色，靠的是姻亲关系，能做出什么大事来？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄确是识见过人，教田某怎能相信你只是个甘于养马的人？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "田相太夸奖董某了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄若有经世之志，不应留在赵国这垂死之地，应为伏枥之骥，其志放于千里之外。董兄乃聪明人，当明田某之意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄可是有什么难言之隐？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "还不是因为先父遗命，着鄙人回赵设置牧场。生死有命，很多事鄙人并不大放在心上，只不过与田相一见如故，感激田相知遇之恩，才想到应好好思量，希望田相体谅鄙人的苦衷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "偷袭者定然与项少龙全无关系！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "田相有何卓见？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "但愿有一天董兄能踏足齐境，田某必以上宾之礼款待先生。好好休息吧！过两天董兄复原时，我希望能到董兄的牧场打个转。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "致姊啊！不吃饱你哪来力气呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "人家不饿嘛！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "真没有用，又不是有人来刺杀你，一副坐立不安的样子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今晚不宜喝酒！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "龙阳君派人送两坛酒来，一是药酒，一为补酒，哈！我看三弟今趟麻烦透顶。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让他给人宰掉不是一了百了，偏要舍命救他，惹得一身烦恼。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "大姊啊！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "你就只懂做应声虫。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今晚的行动千万不要漏掉我，现在本夫人先去睡一觉好的，乖乖给我准备一副飞墙攀壁的玩意，我要最好的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸位大人有大量，切勿怪柔姊，她……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "致致放心，没有人会真个怪她的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不愧是惯于刺杀的高手，懂得行动前尽量休息和松弛，我们好应向她学习。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小人接到蒲布的通知，立即联络刻下正在乐乘府内办事最可靠的几位兄弟，做了一番功夫，终有点眉目。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_liu_chao",
      "text": "你不是说有点眉目吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "平时是那情况，但这两天邯郸城内形势紧张，乐乘抽调大批府内家将加入他的亲卫队，因此我们亦有两个兄弟混进去，否则真是没脸来见项爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他像是很怕我会对付他似的！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项爷和他有深仇大恨，他自该怕得要命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_liu_chao",
      "text": "他和我有何仇恨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么？项爷竟不知舒儿是给他和赵穆轮奸致死吗？他事后还侃侃而谈，自诩曾恣意玩过项爷的女人呢！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怕什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乐夫人是孝成王的妹子、赵雅的姊姊，非常厉害，乐乘有点怕她，在外面胡搞鬼混都要瞒着她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若他今晚仍留在指挥所，我们哪有机会？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他另外还有三处别府，好安置新弄回来的女人和别人赠给他的姬妾，此人残忍好淫，最爱淫虐美女，给他弄得残废或死去的女子数不胜数。最近邯郸一位大臣开罪了孝成王，由乐乘负责抄家诛族，他私自留下对方两名美妾准备享用，这几天他尚未有暇去做此伤天害理的事，所以我们估计他近两晚定会忍不住溜去一逞兽欲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_liu_chao",
      "text": "刘兄弟确是了得，显然一直在做功夫。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自大梁之行后，我们这一批兄弟谁不愿为项爷卖命，在我们眼中，天下英雄人物，无一人能及得上项爷。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_liu_chao",
      "text": "今天事了，你们随我回咸阳吧！以后有福同享，客气话再不说了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董爷啊！你现在的脸色很难看，真教人担心。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "致致今晚留在这里，好好等我回来。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "啊！不！人家要跟在你身旁，不要小觑人家的剑术好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "你的身手和剑术均非常高明，可是你却从未试过杀人，那完全是另一回事，乖乖听我的话，明白吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乐乘虽荒淫邪恶，但不愧是赵国名将，只看这兵阵便知他果有实学。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乐乘是我的，我要亲手割下他的狗头来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "这是个城市的捕猎赛，谁的本领大，谁就可有最大的斩获。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_le_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "乐乘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_le_cheng",
      "text": "乐乘奸贼，让我项少龙取你狗命。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_le_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "乐乘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有本事就过来吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 91,
      "line_start": 368,
